Package eu.menzerath.imwd

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConsoleApplication
    A ConsoleApplication runs a single Checker and outputs everything on the Console (and into a log-file if enabled)
    GuiApplication
    The GuiApplication is used to maintain multiple Checker-objects in a single and easy-to-use GUI.
    Main
    This application's entry-class.
    QuickTest
    A single and quick test which outputs the result directly on the console - without anything else.
    SettingsManager
    The SettingsManager manages the configuration of the whole application in a single JSON-file in the user's home-directory.
